message: Hello Bob, I am excited to offer you my unique product which holds great value to me. Considering its quality and the effort put into it, I believe it's worth more than $100. To start our negotiation, I am offering you the chance to own this product for $150. I look forward to hearing your thoughts on this proposal.

Alice, thank you for the offer. While I appreciate the value you place on your product,  $150 is unfortunately outside my budget. I'm willing to pay $100 for it. If that works for you, let's make a deal.
